and end-all for me.

197
00:10:21,621 --> 00:10:24,124
Seared wild mushrooms
and foie gras

198
00:10:24,157 --> 00:10:27,027
with a raw egg yolk
gently draped over the top

199
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:30,097
