and we play this game.

673
00:38:05,451 --> 00:38:08,420
If you had to die at one
restaurant, you know,

674
00:38:08,454 --> 00:38:10,589
what would your last meal...
What restaurant

675
00:38:10,622 --> 00:38:12,157
