your last meal at?

676
00:38:12,190 --> 00:38:13,825
And they were coming up
with restaurants,

677
00:38:13,859 --> 00:38:15,827
and I said, "Well,
what about Etxe..."

678
00:38:15,861 --> 00:38:17,262
It's Etxebarri?
Etxebarri.

679
00:38:17,295 --> 00:38:19,097
And they all
changed their answer.

680
00:38:19,130 --> 00:38:20,191
They said, "Oh, no, no,
you're right."

681
00:38:20,198 --> 00:38:21,867
That place."

